        embed_id: "4f98a6eb-d40b-4c30-b8af-719c8b5631c6",
        type: "document",
        content: "type: document\napp_id: docs\nskill_id: document\nstatus: finished\ntitle: OpenAI GPT-4o Announcement Summary\nfilename: OpenAI_GPT4o_Summary.docx\nword_count: 244\npage_count: 2\ndocx_model:\n  title: OpenAI GPT-4o Announcement Summary\n  filename: OpenAI_GPT4o_Summary.docx\n  blocks[9]:\n    - type: heading\n      level: 1\n      text: The GPT-4o Announcement\n    - type: paragraph\n      runs[3]:\n        - text: \"On May 13, 2024, OpenAI introduced \"\n        - text: GPT-4o\n          bold: true\n        - text: \" (the 'o' stands for 'omni'), a new flagship model designed for natural human-computer interaction. Unlike previous models that used separate pipelines for voice-to-text and text-to-speech, GPT-4o is trained end-to-end across text, vision, and audio.\"\n    - type: list\n      ordered: false\n      items[4]: \"Speed: Average response time of 320 milliseconds, matching human conversation speed.\",\"Performance: Matches GPT-4 Turbo in English and coding, with significant improvements in non-English languages.\",\"Cost/Efficiency: 50% cheaper and 2x faster in the API compared to GPT-4 Turbo.\",\"Availability: Rolling out to all users, including those on the Free tier (with message limits).\"\n    - type: heading\n      level: 2\n      text: Practical Use Cases\n    - type: paragraph\n      runs[1]{text}:\n        \"The model's ability to 'see' and 'hear' in real time enables several new workflows:\"\n    - type: list\n      ordered: false\n      items[5]: \"Real-Time Translation: Acting as a live translator during conversations or reading menus in foreign languages.\",\"Educational Tutoring: Assisting students by looking at math problems via camera and explaining steps (e.g., Khan Academy demo).\",\"Technical Support & Coding: Using a new desktop app to share screens and troubleshoot code or design in real time.\",\"Emotional Intelligence: Detecting tone of voice and responding with expressive audio, including laughter or singing.\",\"Accessibility: Enhanced support for visually impaired users through tools like Be My Eyes to describe surroundings.\"\n    - type: heading\n      level: 2\n      text: Limitations and Safety\n    - type: paragraph\n      runs[1]{text}:\n        \"OpenAI highlighted several areas where the model is still being refined:\"\n    - type: list\n      ordered: false\n      items[5]: \"Phased Rollout: Advanced audio and video modalities were not released immediately to the public, starting instead with text and image inputs.\",\"Preset Voices: To mitigate risks like deepfaking, audio outputs are initially limited to a small selection of preset voices.\",\"Safety Risks: The model is currently assessed at 'Medium' risk for categories like persuasion and cybersecurity.\",\"Hallucinations: In 'blooper' videos, the model was shown occasionally misinterpreting visual data or providing incorrect answers under specific conditions.\",\"Performance Parity: There are still certain niche tasks where GPT-4 Turbo may outperform GPT-4o, and OpenAI is actively seeking feedback on these cases.\"\ndocx_s3_key: chatfiles/50c1a4b9-cad1-4ea9-bc2a-fc7c616d8293/20260607_222558_3899880b_doc_4f98a6eb.docx.bin\nscreenshot_s3_keys:\n  \\1\\: chatfiles/50c1a4b9-cad1-4ea9-bc2a-fc7c616d8293/20260607_222558_3899880b_doc_4f98a6eb_p1.png.bin\n  \\2\\: chatfiles/50c1a4b9-cad1-4ea9-bc2a-fc7c616d8293/20260607_222558_3899880b_doc_4f98a6eb_p2.png.bin\naes_key: vhEX4osoKScVjUBI6whBeXT95dL0vapbHI9R2rwLBBI=\naes_nonce: \"\"\nvault_wrapped_aes_key: \"vault:v1:sWbCZfcV15aWRY+WrP/JA+W53+GBVkdNCIM7e7x+61AVtnptedR4N+n5cfB9iWSOkdFNOKEdvi03umd1Z+I4+B2cpaRz4EMn\"",
